{"tid":1831148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎巴嫩反政府示威400傷","createTime":"2020-01-20T07:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T11:47:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a35dcfef7e34d8a5a51e974b7fa1e96adee03217","tid":1831148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200120/YBP3ZKO6OYRZIIBVVEAD3C6VGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200120%2FYBP3ZKO6OYRZIIBVVEAD3C6VGA%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9yBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=58916e57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200120%2FYBP3ZKO6OYRZIIBVVEAD3C6VGA%2F&h=7fc5c8d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200120/YBP3ZKO6OYRZIIBVVEAD3C6VGA/</a><br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩反政府示威400傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200120/large/1579449128_6b82.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579449128_6b82.gif&h=848a41f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員向示威者發射催淚氣體。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩反政府示威仍未平息，前日首都貝魯特的示威演變成嚴重警民衝突，近400人受傷，是示威浪潮爆發三個月以來最多。<br />\n<br />\n保安隊水炮 催淚彈還擊<br />\n<br />\n示威者抗議掌控國家的精英階層無法改善經濟問題，示威最先由數十名用頸巾蒙面的示威者向警察投擲石塊，另一批示威者則手持路牌、金屬欄杆和樹枝當武器，衝擊封鎖國會大樓附近通道的防暴警察。保安部隊出動水炮及催淚彈還擊。國營國家通訊社報道，約30人被捕後獲釋。內政部長哈桑表示，不能接受有示威者毆打保安部隊。另外，保安部隊稱正調查一段網上影片，相信是示威者被帶到貝魯特警署後遭警員毆打。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩去年10月起爆發大規模反政府示威，總理哈里里在壓力下同月辭職。示威者未有因此停止抗議，批評當局腐敗行為猖獗，處事無效率，以及只在乎個人及黨派利益。總統奧恩在12月任命前教育部長迪亞卜為新總理，惟各政黨出現嚴重分歧，未能成功籌組新政府，加上國家財政狀況持續惡化，民眾不滿官員腐敗及管治不力，互聯網繼續有人號召在國會附近示威。世界銀行警告，若不盡快解決黎巴嫩政府危機，當地貧窮率可能由目前的三分一，增至一半。<br />\n<br />\n法新社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200120/large/1579449129_d651.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579449129_d651.gif&h=b6f13a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者無懼警方向他們發射水炮。"},{"pid":"acf924400a84bb5f54667d9c00dea190fb93a2cf","tid":1831148,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"e2d077cc43381d6645544c074187dd78dc84cc96","tid":1831148,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:45:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5649a4ee7be41ebace964dc7a0043ad284068c22","tid":1831148,"uid":91771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"黎巴嫩係少數中東嘅清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1471a3418a053f036f1a9e7b8632dcd977a408","tid":1831148,"uid":105232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"天下黑警一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7372bb1d2e144add2ec4976d8adadb09853e4e87","tid":1831148,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f1471a3418a053f036f1a9e7b8632dcd977a408","tid":1831148,"uid":105232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"天下黑警一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:44:53.000Z","msg":"又唔可以咁講<br />\n黎巴嫩示威者衝擊 防暴警察 , 所以防暴警察 還擊是合情合理<br />\n<br />\n而香港就是 示威者 和平集會, 但遭到防暴警察 武力鎮壓, 所以香港警察先會被人叫黑警"},{"pid":"0ff6a2cded66e71339126e04bf615109e8d84614","tid":1831148,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"黑警係一個跨國物種，一樣都係咁仆街"}]}